conditional statements
true or false
1. if
	simple if
		if (condition)
			statement_true;
		if (condition)
			statement_true;	
	if else
		if (condition)
			statement_true;	
		else
			statement_false;	
	if else if else
		if (condition_1)
			statement_1;
		else if (condition2)
			statement_2;
		else if (condition3)
			statement_3;
		else if (condition_n)
			statement_n;
		else
			statement;
	nested if
2. switch statement 

Relational operators -> <,<=,>,>=,==,!=
Logical operators -> AND OR NOT
